{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AFZpGLWriQpEPPtV8u9ydC","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t// /operations/queue — Event queue admin page (FR-10).\n2\t//\n3\t// Reads `event_queue` (migration 009) via `get-event-queue.ts` and composes:\n4\t//\n5\t//   - Metric strip   — pending / processing / failed / dead / at_max_attempts\n6\t//                      / aged_pending. Failed and dead counts double as the\n7\t//                      attention links called out by FR-10 (drilldown to\n8\t//                      `?status=failed` / `?status=dead`).\n9\t//   - Status + type breakdown — full status distribution and the top 50\n10\t//                      event types by frequency, so an operator can see which\n11\t//                      event_type is generating the dead/failed pile.\n12\t//   - Filter bar     — status, event type, id, payload user id, scheduled +\n13\t//                      created date windows, age bucket. URL-addressable\n14\t//                      (`queueFilter*`).\n15\t//   - Filtered table — bounded list with a row-level link that sets\n16\t//                      `?selectedId=<id>` to open the detail panel.\n17\t//   - Detail panel   — full payload rendered with secret redaction applied\n18\t//                      server-side (`redactJsonValue` / `redactNullableString`\n19\t//                      from the audit module).\n20\t//\n21\t// Read-only — retry / cancel / replay are explicitly out of scope (FR-10\n22\t// line 342) and live behind a future mutation spec.\n23\timport type { CSSProperties } from \"react\";\n24\timport { EventQueueDetailPanel } from \"../../../src/components/event-queue-detail-panel\";\n25\timport { EventQueueFilterBar } from \"../../../src/components/event-queue-filter-bar\";\n26\timport { EventQueueTable } from \"../../../src/components/event-queue-table\";\n27\timport { MetricStrip } from \"../../../src/components/metric-strip\";\n28\timport {\n29\t  normalizeEventQueueFiltersFromS